title: KCRW.com - Top Tunes May 2008
description:
Collected from KCRW.com as their free daily download.  MP3 format, quality ranges from 64KBPS (what? some new guy at the station probably) to 128KPBS, a few files are even higher as I was forced to get files from secondary sources (new guy didn&#039;t show up for work), 44KHz.  Files are uniformly named with embedded album covers and M3U playlist.

If you like what you hear, I strongly urge you to join KCRW as a member or donate to the station (KCRW.com or at 89.9 FM in the LA area).  Enjoy!
